data.description: This fully renovated gem boasts 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 sleek bathrooms, and a versatile den perfect for a home office or play area. Soaring vaulted ceilings, crown moldings, and stylish wood blinds create a sense of opulence. The showstopper kitchen impresses with granite countertops, high-end appliances, and a smart refrigerator. Both bathrooms are tastefully updated with new tile flooring and wall tiles. With brand-new AC units (2022) controlled by a smart Nest thermostat. Additional features include hurricane impact windows, accordion shutters, rain gutters, a front and back sprinkler system, and lush landscaping. This smart home also comes equipped with front and back Ring cameras and keyless garage entry. Unbeatable location moments from Hard Rock Stadium and Hard Rock Hotel.
